headline.print_headline: GE Says Infrastructure Demand to Boost Orders for Developing Markets
headline.main: GE Says Infrastructure Demand to Boost Orders for Developing Markets

lead_paragraph: General Electric Co expects developing markets to be a "huge engine" of growth due to demand for the company's products that provide infrastructure in these countries, GE's top international executive said on Wednesday.
